quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  36,1,"Ya'. Sin."{1},footnotes:1:1
  36,2,"By the Wise Qur'an,"
  36,3,"you are truly among the Messengers,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  36,4,"on a Straight Way,"
  36,5,"(and this Qur'an) is a revelation from the Most Mighty, the Most Compassionate"{1},footnotes:1:1
  36,6,"so that you may warn a people whose ancestors were not warned before wherefore they are heedless."{1},footnotes:1:1
  36,7,"Surely most of them merit the decree of chastisement; so they do not believe."{1},footnotes:1:1
  36,8,"We have put fetters around their necks which reach up to their chins so that they are standing with their heads upright,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  36,9,"and We have put a barrier before them and a barrier behind them, and have covered them up, so they are unable to see."{1},footnotes:1:1
  36,10,"It is all the same for them whether you warn them or do not warn them for they shall not believe."{1},footnotes:1:1